title: Classification (System Upload Format)
description: This zip-file is used to transfer the classication to the S/4 System by uploading it using the Report ZKNSF_CLASSIFICATION_MANAGR

title: Classifications (External Sharing Format)
description: This zip-file is used to either backup the classification or transfer it to another Kernseife BTP Tenant.

title: Missing Classifications
description: Exports the Classification for objects which exist in the Cloudification Repository, but not in your Kernseife tenant. This needs a specical connection to an S/4 System and is not meant for public usage.
